{
  "stem": "3933.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she was such a good-- a very good measurement.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she was average-- not little, not-- And I gave her this breast, and she was nursing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we made a pact that he's going to put her away in a nursing home-- in a findling home.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I'll never forget when he took the child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The midwife left-- whatever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She didn't-- he didn't pay her, and she did it for being a Catholic-- good Christian-- whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I'll never forget when the child-- he told me-- being an invalid, and walking with a cane, couldn't he [INAUDIBLE]-- very fast, he was back, without her.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Very, very fast!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He couldn't go to the findling home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I know it was too far.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And walking the way he walks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He was holding the cane and the other hand holding this little, beautiful child.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I didn't know nothing anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't talk about it, and I wouldn't even ask him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I told him, did you put it there?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, I told you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes-- don't ask me--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By the way, my son wasn't with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Another thing-- I have to go back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "These few days, my brother-in-law-- my brother-in-law, the non-Jewish brother-in-law-- took him by-- took him to his wife, where she was hiding, in a little village.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Got a good hiding place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They paid them, and they got food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is the biggest [INAUDIBLE] was I, the one who was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then he wasn't around, my son, with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was so glad he couldn't just be stuck-- stick to me like he did.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And anyway, I recovered in a few days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I wasn't thinking, even, because I was facing, the-- and the situation was-- I wasn't-- I must admit I wasn't thinking about the baby.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
